title: I didn't recieve the poro icon

replies.body: The icons and gifts are not done being sent out, so hang tight!  You can bookmark our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-) on our current progress.   It will take some time, but everyone eligible will get the goods!
